args: Whoa, the sunset is super pretty today!
It's also pleasantly cool—unlike how\nit was in the middle of the day.
Oh, I was just having a little think\nwhile enjoying the sea breeze.
Wait, YOU were having a think?\nThe lady who does nothing but run around\nand scream about training all the time?
Holy crap, everybody look out\nfor the flying pigs!
Even I need to think sometimes!
So what were you thinking about?
About how much fun I've had\nhere at the beach.
You told me that I should try to enjoy\nbeing here in my own way.
And thanks to that, I managed to have\na ball of a time with my training.
I doubt it would have been half\nas fun if I'd come on my own.
I'm just glad you enjoyed yourself.
The castle is full of fine people—\nincluding you, of course.
You're always joining me in my training,\nand letting me off when I cause trouble.
I'm so glad I came to the Halidom!
We could say the same to you.
We've all become stronger because of\nyour training regimens, and you've made\nthe castle a much livelier place to boot.
We're all glad to have you with us.
I am not! That's just the sun!
Hee hee! No need for the tough-girl act.
Stop looking at me and look at the\nsunset instead, damn it!
Watch it sinking below the horizon\nand feel youthful! That's an order!
Er, I mean, of course! If you want my\ncompany, I'd be happy to give it.
It's no surprise after how much playing—\nEr, I mean, TRAINING that she's done.
We were just sitting here watching the\nsunset. It must've gotten the better of her.
Heh. She is like a child worn out after\na long day at the beach.
Can we let her sleep a little more?
I would feel guilty waking her now.
I'll leave looking after her to you,\nYour Highness.
Perhaps Cleo will be willing to\ndelay dinner a little while longer.
Oh man, she looks super innocent.\nI wonder what she's dreaming about?
Zzz... The pain is just starting, kiddos...\nDon't whine now... Zzzz...
Dude, she even cracks the whip\nin her SLEEP!
